data.description: Welcome to your potential dream home in Citrus Springs, this charming and inviting home has 3 bedroom, 2 bathrooms with 1400 SQ Ft of space and a split floor plan is ready to make it your own and achieve perfection! from the moment yo step inside, you'll be greeted by a welcoming and inviting atmosphere. Situated in a desirable location, this property offers the best of both worlds, its conveniently in short distance to shopping and dinning yet it stills provide a peaceful and rural feel of living. Nature lovers will be happy with the close proximity to Crystal River and Rainbow river as well as trails. This home is a great option for first time buyers who are eager to relocate closer to nature and enjoy outdoor activities. Don't miss the chance to turn this house into your ideal home, where you can create new memories and enjoy the tranquil beauty of Citrus Springs. NEW ROOF TO BE INSTALLED BEFORE CLOSING!
